HEADWORD: Locustic
<hw>Lo*cus"tic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to, or derived from, the locust; -- formerly used to
designate a supposed acid.</def>⟦br⟧
